### Register User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "honey",
  "password": "StrongPass123"
}

### Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "<your-refresh-token>"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

{
  "refreshToken": "<your-refresh-token>"
}

### Verify OTP
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "<session-id>",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### Verify Email
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "verificationToken": "<verification-token>"
}

### Forgot Password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "honey@example.com"
}

### Reset Password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resetToken": "<reset-token>",
  "newPassword": "NewStrongPass123"
}

### Resend Verification Email
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/resend-verification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "honey@example.com"
}

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/health
